views.createSql:
CREATE VIEW `${VIEW_NAME}` AS SELECT packageName   AS packageName,
               SUM(count)          AS totalCount
        FROM   download_stats
        WHERE client = '_total'
        GROUP BY packageName

CREATE VIEW `${VIEW_NAME}` AS SELECT packageName   AS packageName,
               client              AS client,
               SUM(count)          AS totalCount
        FROM   download_stats
        GROUP BY packageName, client

CREATE VIEW `${VIEW_NAME}` AS SELECT packageName      AS packageName,
               client                 AS client,
               (isoDate / 100)  AS yearMonth,
               SUM(count)             AS totalCount
        FROM   download_stats
        GROUP BY packageName, client, yearMonth

CREATE VIEW `${VIEW_NAME}` AS SELECT mg.packageName   AS packageName,
               mg.icon           AS icon,
               mg.metadataIcon  AS metadataIcon
        FROM   product_v2 AS mg
        JOIN (
            SELECT   packageName, MAX(updated) AS latest
            FROM     product_v2
            GROUP BY packageName
        ) AS sg
        ON mg.packageName = sg.packageName AND mg.updated = sg.latest
